Description: =============================
        Django User Assets
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-user-assets.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-user-assets
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/idaproject/django-user-assets.svg?branch=master
